comments: Embiid (PHI) establishes himself in a screening position in LeVert's (CLE) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Markkanen (CLE) places his hands against Embiid's (PHI) body in the lane and slides his hands off as he gathers the rebound.
Stevens (CLE) briefly places his hands against Embiid's (PHI) side after gathering the rebound.
Stevens (CLE) places his forearm to Embiid's (PHI) front during his drive and marginal contact occurs.
Okoro (CLE) places his arm against Embiid's (PHI) front after his gather, and makes marginal contact as he slides his arm off defending his driving shot attempt.
Garland (CLE) briefly places his hand against Harris' (PHI) arm off ball and removes it as he gathers the inbound pass.
Stevens (CLE) jumps from point A to point B and makes contact with Harris' (PHI) body that affects his shot attempt at the basket.
Stevens (CLE) is already in Maxey's (PHI) path as he sets the pick and releases away from the contact as they disengage.
Harden (PHI) is in the paint for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Harden (PHI) makes contact with Garland's (CLE) arm after he gathers the rebound and the contact affects his SQBR.
Harden (PHI) makes marginal contact with LeVert (CLE) as they move up the court at the start of the possession.
Embiid (PHI) establishes himself in a screening position in LeVert's (CLE) path and does not deliver contact.
Garland (CLE) fails to fully clear the lane and is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Stevens (CLE) makes marginal contact with Harden's (PHI) body after the release of his driving shot attempt.
Maxey (PHI) makes contact with Garland's (CLE) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Stevens (CLE) briefly places his forearm to Harris' (PHI) front at the start of his drive and the contact is marginal.
Stevens (CLE) legally contests Harris (PHI) drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Stevens (CLE) establishes himself in a screening position in Thybulle's (PHI) path and does not deliver contact.
While defending his drive to the basket and shot attempt, Embiid (PHI) reaches across Garland (CLE) and makes contact to his left arm.

Stevens (CLE) makes incidental contact with Harden's (PHI) head after applying defensive pressure in the backcourt after the rebound.  Contact to an opponent's head/face can be deemed marginal when the result of a natural basketball move, provided the contact is not disproportionate or uncontrolled.
While off-ball, Harden (PHI) places his hand on Markkanen's (CLE) back and hooks his arm during the inbound.
Niang (PHI) inbounds the ball under 5 seconds.
Markkanen (CLE) commits a take foul on Harden (PHI).
Harden (PHI) briefly engages with LeVert (CLE) prior to the screen.
Stevens (CLE) establishes himself in a screening position in Thybulle's (PHI) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Love (CLE) inbounds the ball within 5 seconds.
Thybulle (PHI) cleanly deflects the inbound pass to Garland (CLE) before incidental contact occurs.
Garland (CLE) and Thybulle (PHI) engage and disengage with one another as they pursue the loose ball.
Stevens (CLE) establishes himself in a screening position in Harden's (PHI) path and makes marginal contact to his side as they disengage.
Harden (PHI) places his forearm to LeVert's (CLE) front during his drive to the basket and marginal contact occurs.
Love (CLE) commits a take foul on Embiid (PHI).
